    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The recurrent neural network (RNN) layer initialized with a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/metalperformanceshaders/mpsgrudescriptor",
              "isActive": false,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " transforms the input data (image or matrix) and previous output with a set of filters. Each produces one feature map in the output data according to the gated recurrent unit (GRU) unit formula detailed below. ",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You may provide the GRU unit with a single input or a sequence of inputs. The layer also supports p-norm gating.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "2888086",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Description of Operation",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "x_j",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be the input data (at time index ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "t",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " of sequence, ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "j",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " index containing quadruplet: batch index, ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "x,y",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " and feature index (",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "x = y = 0",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " for matrices)).",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "h0_",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "j be the recurrent input (previous output) data from previous time step (at time index ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "t-1",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " of sequence).",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "h_i",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be the proposed new output.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "h1_i",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be the output data produced at this time step.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "Wz_ij",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "Uz_ij",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be the input gate weights for input and recurrent input data, respectively.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "bi_i",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be the bias for the input gate.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "Wr_ij",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "Ur_ij",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be the recurrent gate weights for input and recurrent input data, respectively.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "br_i",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be the bias for the recurrent gate.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "Wh_ij",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "Uh_ij",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "Vh_ij",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be the output gate weights for input, recurrent gate, and input gate, respectively.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "bh_i",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be the bias for the output gate.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "gz(x",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": ")",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "gr(x)",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "gh(x)",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be the neuron activation function for the input, recurrent, and output gates.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Let ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "p > 0",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " be a scalar variable (typical ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "p >= 1.0",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ") that defines the p-norm gating norm value.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The output of the GRU layer is computed as follows:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "z_i = gz(  Wz_ij * x_j  +  Uz_ij * h0_j  +  bz_i  )",
            "r_i = gr(  Wr_ij * x_j  +  Ur_ij * h0_j  +  br_i  )",
            "c_i =      Uh_ij * (r_j h0_j)  +  Vh_ij * (z_j h0_j)",
            "h_i = gh(  Wh_ij * x_j  + c_i + bh_i  )",
            "",
            "h1_i = ( 1 - z_i ^ p)^(1/p) h0_i + z_i h_i"
          ],
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "2888087",
            "title": "Listing 1"
          },
          "syntax": "other",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "*",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " stands for convolution (see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/metalperformanceshaders/mpsrnnimageinferencelayer",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ") or matrix-vector/matrix multiplication (see ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/metalperformanceshaders/mpsrnnmatrixinferencelayer",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ").",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Summation is over index ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "j",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " (except for the batch index), but there's no summation over repeated index ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "i",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ",",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": " ",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": "the output index.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Note that for validity, all intermediate images must be of same size, and all ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "U",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " and ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "V",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " matrices must be square (that is, ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/metalperformanceshaders/mpsrnndescriptor/2865702-outputfeaturechannels",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "code": " ==",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/metalperformanceshaders/mpsrnndescriptor/2865707-inputfeaturechannels",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": "). Also, the bias terms are scalars with regard to spatial dimensions. The conventional GRU block is achieved by setting ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "Vh = 0",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " (nil), and the Minimal Gated Unit is achieved with ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "Uh = 0",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
